{"tid":569430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又得分] 貪心警疑知法犯法 順手牽羊偷櫃員機8千蚊","createTime":"2018-02-22T16:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T00:09:27.000Z","uid":54337,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb75ae329bead6e8d3e5986584f6156b235472c","tid":569430,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"貪心警疑知法犯法 順手牽羊偷櫃員機8千蚊<br />\n<br />\n2018-02-22 21:46:48 HKT<br />\n<br />\n一名警員懷疑知法犯法，去年7月4日在九龍城福佬村道18號一銀行櫃員機，涉嫌盜取他人提款後忘記取走的約8,000元現金。九龍城警區重案組人員接手調查案件，昨午4時30分在跑馬地警署拘捕38歲姓劉男警，涉嫌盜竊，他已獲准保釋候查，須於3月中旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180222/57863634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57863634&d=ZRIXzU2NY6P31ttKCpkdv9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ec991ffa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57863634&h=671d883a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180222/57863634</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pbh2.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/beautiful-goals-chicharito.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbh2.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F12%2Fbeautiful-goals-chicharito.gif&h=63b87d5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dda8a39868ef58e0630a0d012679782467ee2ff","tid":569430,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f01895af0fae1d7d9bb927daf29874bfeb5dcc0","tid":569430,"uid":161709,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018